title: [Reticent Repose, Breakfast Nook]
description: Terra cotta-colored walls complement pale sandstone tile floors in variegated neutral tones.  Muted moonlight gently illuminates a rosewood table through a latched garden window adorned with drawn ivory and sunset orange linen curtains.  Twin sconces cast dancing shadows upon an enameled iron stove set against a far wall adjacent to an intimate maoral booth tucked into the corner.
room.location: Reticent Repose, inside the elven fortress of Ta'Vaalor
